    "_comment": "Declarative map of which source document yields which cost-sheet field. Drives OCR/data-entry templates. `anchors` are BEST-GUESS candidate label strings (English + Amharic) seen on Ethiopian customs/bank/clearing paperwork — confirm/trim them against the real scans (matching is case-insensitive, substring). `target` is the Import Shipment fieldname (or charges[].description for a ledger line) and MUST NOT change — it ties to STANDARD_CHARGE_TEMPLATE in import_shipment.py.",
